### Get all categories
GET http://localhost:8081/api/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get category by id
GET http://localhost:8081/api/categories/{{categoryId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Search categories by name
GET http://localhost:8081/api/categories/search?keyword=k
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Search categories by subcategory name
