Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create new category
POST http://localhost:8081/api/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "categoryName": "Socola trendy"
}

### Update category
PATCH http://localhost:8081/api/categories/{{categoryId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "categoryName": "Socola xu hướng"
}

### Delete category
DELETE http://localhost:8081/api/categories/{{categoryId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get subcategories by category id
GET http://localhost:8081/api/categories/{{categoryId}}/subcategories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}} 